==English==

===Proper Noun===
'''Capulet'''

#A member of [[Juliet]]'s family in William [[Shakespeare]]'s ''Romeo & Juliet''.
#(''Figurative'') By analogy with the Shakespearean play, a member or citizen of the family, party, or country of the wife in a [[Romeo and Juliet couple]].

